Supported endpoints:

1: Stations status
PATH: /health/stations
METHOD: GET
Response example:
{
  "err": false,
  "stations": [
    {
      "active": true,
      "id": 81,
      "running": true
    }
  ]
}

2: Restart all ices modules
PATH: /station/restart
METHOD: POST
Response example:
{
  "err": false,
  [
  "name": "Deep",
  "stream_url"
}

3: Restart ices module with id
PATH: /station/restart/<int:id>
METHOD: POST
Response example:
{
  "err": false,
  "status": "ok"
}

4: Active stations
PATH: /station
METHOD: GET
Response example:
{
  "err": false,
  "stations": [
    {
      "name": "Deep",
      "stream_url": "https://stream.mistofm.com.ua/deep",
      "metadata_url": "https://metadata.mistofm.com.ua/metadata/get/3",
    }
  ]
}

Handle errors:
If there is an error, the server will return json in following format:
{"error":true, "message":"Not found", code:404}
